♪Mula sa sandaling ito, wala na akong pakialam♪

00:31:18.940 --> 00:31:21.260
♪Wala nang ingay sa tenga ko♪

00:31:22.300 --> 00:31:25.660
♪Iyan ang kapayapaang
lagi kong inaasam♪

00:31:26.300 --> 00:31:28.420
♪Para kanino ko sinubukang baguhin?♪

00:31:28.420 --> 00:31:31.900
♪Ngumiti, umiiyak, nagrereklamo♪

00:31:32.500 --> 00:31:39.460
♪Iyan ang kasiyahang
dapat kong matutunang yakapin♪

00:31:39.580 --> 00:31:43.060
♪Sa totoo lang, wala akong pakialam♪

00:31:43.060 --> 00:31:46.820
♪Ilang beses mo na akong nasaktan♪

00:31:46.820 --> 00:31:50.380
♪Ang tinatawag mong taos-pusong debosyon♪

00:31:50.420 --> 00:31:53.940
♪Baka manhid lang ako♪

00:31:54.020 --> 00:31:57.460
♪Sa totoo lang, wala akong pakialam♪

00:31:57.540 --> 00:32:00.860
♪Kahit naligaw ako♪

